<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٧٩٥٤]</span> عُمرُ بنُ تِيرِي <span class="c2">(٢)</span> الصَّنْعانيُّ <span class="c2">(٣)</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>سَمِعَ هانِئًا.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>سَمِعَ مِنهُ ابنُ المُبارَكِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>مُنقَطِعٌ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
